high_descs: Turn around, then begin walking to the door, hang a right and walk up to the fridge, then turn right again and walk over to where the toaster is on the counter.
Pick up the metal spoon that is to the right of the toaster on the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the metal spoon inside the white mug that is in the fridge.
Remove the white mug with the spoon inside of it from the fridge and close the fridge door.
Turn right and walk over to the section of counter above the dishwasher.
Place the mug with the spoon inside of it onto the front edge of the counter just above the middle of the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon inside of it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go straight, turn right, turn right at the refrigerator, move forward, then turn left to face the counter with the dishwasher.
Pick up the spoon on the counter, to the right of the toaster.
Turn left, go forward, then turn right to go to the fridge.
Put the spoon in the mug inside of the fridge.
Pick up the mug with the spoon in it from in the fridge.
Turn right, go forward, then turn left to return to the counter above the dishwasher.
Put the mug with the spoon in it on the counter, to the right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk in front of the counter with the toaster on it.
Pick up the spoon that's next to the toaster.
Move to the front of the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the spoon in the white mug.
Take the mug out of the fridge and close the door.
Turn to the right and stand in front of the counter with two heads of lettuce on it.
Put the mug down on the edge of the counter.
anns.task_desc: To get a chilled mug for coffee.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn right and walk to the fridge then take a step to your right.
Pick up the spoon that's in front of you.
Take a step to your left.
Put  the spoon in the mug in the fridge.
Pick up the mug with the spoon in it and close the door.
Take two steps to your right.
Put the mug to the left of the head of lettuce nearest the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon in it on the counter.

high_descs: Cross the room to face the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick the spoon up from the counter.
Move to the left and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the spoon in the cup.
Pick the cup up from inside the fridge.
Turn and go to face the counter to the right of the fridge.
Put the cup on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a spoon in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, head in to the kitchen
Stand in front of the counter next to the fridge
Take the spoon from the counter
Go to the fridge, open the door
Put the spoon inside the white mug inside the fridge
Take the white mug out of the fridge, close the door
Turn right, walk in to kitchen, put the white mug on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon inside a white mug, place the mug on the counter
